---
<section id="deploy" class="bg-[#0a0a0a] py-16">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">Choose your path</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-gray-400">
        ragweld is open source and self-hostable — and we also support enterprise deployments.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-[#222] bg-[#0f0f0f] p-6">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#00ff88]">Open source</div>
        <h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-bold text-white">Self-hosted / on-prem</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
          MIT licensed. Run it on your infrastructure. Keep your corpora, embeddings, and model traffic where you want
          them.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
          <li>• Tribrid retrieval: vector + sparse + graph</li>
          <li>• Benchmark + eval suites with run comparisons</li>
          <li>• Deep config + parameter glossary + tooltips</li>
          <li>• Multi-corpus + per-corpus overrides</li>
          <li>• Learning reranker: LoRA training + yes/no logits scoring</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a
            href="https://dmontgomery40.github.io/tribrid-rag/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-[#00ff88] text-black font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-[#00dd77] transition-colors"
          >
            Docs
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/DMontgomery40/tribrid-rag"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="px-5 py-2.5 border border-[#333] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-[#111] transition-colors"
          >
            GitHub
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-[#222] bg-[#0f0f0f] p-6">
        <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#5b9dff]">Enterprise</div>
        <h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-bold text-white">Managed deployments + custom integrations</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
          For teams pushing RAG into production: deployment patterns, hardened ops, and integration work tailored to your
          stack.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
          <li>• Cloud or on-prem deployments (your network, your controls)</li>
          <li>• Observability + alerting hooks that plug into your on-call</li>
          <li>• Benchmarks/evals as a release gate (regressions don’t ship)</li>
          <li>• MCP + automation workflows for agents and internal tools</li>
          <li>• Trainable reranking on Apple Silicon (MLX) + Linux fallback</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a
            href="mailto:david@ragweld.com?subject=ragweld%20Enterprise%20Inquiry"
            class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-[#5b9dff] text-black font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-[#4a8cf2] transition-colors"
          >
            Contact enterprise
          </a>
          <a
            href="/demo/?corpus=faxbot"
            class="px-5 py-2.5 border border-[#333] text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-[#111] transition-colors"
          >
            Launch demo
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
